This directory (test_Ar_periodic_FCC_NEIGH_RVEC_f90) contains a test that computes the
energy per atom in an infinite perfect FCC crystal of Argon using the NEIGH-RVEC-F NBC.
(The test uses a one atom configuration and constructs a neighbor list with multiple
images of this one atom.)

Makefile                                -- makefile to compile and build executables with
                                           GNU or Intel compilers
README                                  -- this file 
test_Ar_periodic_FCC_NEIGH_RVEC_f90.F90 -- Code for the test
test_Ar_periodic_FCC_NEIGH_RVEC_f90.kim -- KIM descriptor file for the test

